son\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shericka_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 205, \"end\": 211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.590043633254998, \"rank\": 0.6725145548100431, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chef de Mission\", \"from\": 11, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's injured star sprinters\", \"from\": 82, \"to\": 118}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 176, \"to\": 197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kelly toldObserver Onlinethat Fraser-Pryce, a two-time Olympic champion and the team captain, departed the village earlier this week, while Jackson left on Thursday.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999999433190412, \"rank\": 5.4767360340573584e-08, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 362, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackson_Guitars\", \"score\": 0.5466395528582061, \"rank\": 0.6940455601021313, \"text\": \"Jackson\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackson_Guitars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackson_Guitars\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Onlinethat Fraser-Pryce\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-time Olympic champion\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"the team captain\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Shelly-Ann left the village earlier this week, and Shericka left just today.\", \"fro